# ===== NOLIMIT ELECTRON APP - CONFIGURATION =====

# Approval Server URL
# Where approval requests are sent for admin approval
# 
# Development (local):
VITE_APPROVAL_SERVER=http://localhost:3001
#
# Production (after deploying on Render/Vercel):
# VITE_APPROVAL_SERVER=https://nolimit-approval.onrender.com

# Notes:
# - All product, stock, and movement data is stored locally in IndexedDB
# - Only approval requests are sent to this server
# - App works completely offline, syncs when online
# - No other configuration needed for basic functionality
